methods.makeToDoubleCast:
Create a kernel that casts the values in an input chunk to an double.

:param type: (io.deephaven.engine.chunk.ChunkType) - the type of chunk, must be an integral primitive type
:param size: (int) - the size of the largest chunk that can be cast by this kernel
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.v2.utils.cast.ToDoubleCast) a ToIntFunctor that can be applied to chunks of type in order to produce a DoubleChunk of values
